{"tid":1852213,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【全盛時期既支那狗可以有幾撚自私？】 曾住W酒店 武漢夫婦不太合作　行程未能確實","createTime":"2020-01-30T10:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T10:55:16.000Z","uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b44308e3e9684771aa22591d67f5b26f042221c7","tid":1852213,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nL9DBQW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnL9DBQW.gif&h=1389d9e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nL9DBQW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnL9DBQW.gif&h=1389d9e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nL9DBQW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnL9DBQW.gif&h=1389d9e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nL9DBQW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnL9DBQW.gif&h=1389d9e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nL9DBQW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnL9DBQW.gif&h=1389d9e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nL9DBQW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnL9DBQW.gif&h=1389d9e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nL9DBQW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnL9DBQW.gif&h=1389d9e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nL9DBQW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnL9DBQW.gif&h=1389d9e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nL9DBQW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnL9DBQW.gif&h=1389d9e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nL9DBQW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnL9DBQW.gif&h=1389d9e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當局指確診新型肺炎武漢夫婦不太合作 行程未能確實<br />\n本港至今有10宗新型冠狀病毒確診感染個案，最新2宗個案是一對來自武漢的夫婦。衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君表示，連同夫婦的一名家人，及2人到訪過2間酒店、接觸過的5名酒店職員，合共6人被列為他們的密切接觸者，現正接受隔離。<br />\n<br />\n張竹君透露，2人本月22日乘坐飛機到港，隨即入住過W酒店，數天後又轉住四季酒店，但最後只在該酒店逗留數小時，之後不適送院。她說，2人不太合作，因此未能得知他們在港期間，確實到過甚麼地方，只知道期間到過一些餐廳食飯，多數時間留在酒店。<br />\n<br />\n至於目前情況嚴重的確診病人，是56歲、本港第二位確診患者。醫管局總行政經理莊慧敏表示，病人需要提供氧氣協助，亦要接受藥物治療，醫管局已邀請港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇，以及中大呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n對於有傳伊利沙伯醫院深切治療部有醫護人員，因為抽中要照顧懷疑及確診感染新型冠狀病毒的病人，於是離職，莊慧敏說，要向人力資源部瞭解。另外她強調，如果醫護人員因為照顧過懷疑或確診病人需要接受隔離，該段時間不會被扣減病假。被問到有否發現，有醫院向員工提供過期口罩，莊慧敏說，暫時未有從醫護人員收到涉及過期口罩的投訴，相信過期機會不大"},{"pid":"e9e1a59ab1606665f0b1ec828160b70a508d6902","tid":1852213,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:51:48.000Z","msg":"封關前走到 又住5星酒店<br />\n唔係有錢就係做官 <br />\n分分鐘見完中聯辦或解放軍唔可以講"},{"pid":"a4d6c5f46efeaf45e518cf29fc0769a6a892e289","tid":1852213,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9e1a59ab1606665f0b1ec828160b70a508d6902","tid":1852213,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:51:48.000Z","msg":"封關前走到 又住5星酒店<br />\n唔係有錢就係做官 <br />\n分分鐘見完中聯辦或解放軍唔可以講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:53:13.000Z","msg":"突破盲撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"417609b319c1124c51b605b3c32315e76064c5c4","tid":1852213,"uid":112241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:55:16.000Z","msg":"唔通同你地如實講，男既去左叫雞，女既叫鴨呀？"}]}